Description:
You arrive at a crowded island with a large hut at the center, where a man dressed in scuba gear is serving people. When you speak to him, he introduces himself as Dale and apologizes for the lack of available tables, but he offers the option to order something to take away. 

He specializes in dishes made from freshly caught sea ingredients. 

Dale also expresses interest in purchasing various eccentric items and mentions his affiliation with several trade organizations.
DescriptionAction: Would you like to order any of his dishes or sell him something?
